Package io.opencaesar.oml

Interface StructureInstance

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, Instance, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StructureInstanceImpl
    public interface StructureInstance
extends Instance
    A representation of the model object 'Structure Instance'. StructureInstance is an instance that can be typed by a structure. It is anonymous and gets assigned as a value for structured properties, either as part of value restrictions on entities, or value assertions on instances.

    The following features are supported:

    • Type
    • Owning Axiom
    • Owning Assertion
